What if my question is still not answered?
   </title>
   <para>
Please check the offical mame and mess readme files to see if that answers your question:
   </para>
   <itemizedlist>
    <listitem>
    <para>
<ulink url="readme.mame">The official mame readme file (readme.mame)</ulink>
    </para>

   </listitem>
    <listitem>
    <para>
<ulink url="readme.mess">The official mess readme file (readme.mess)</ulink>
    </para>

   </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>
   <para>
If that doesn't help, then ask your question on the mailing list or send it to the xmame/xmess maintainer, see  <link linkend="Mail">Mail</link> for contact information.
   </para>

